{"id":"273067571_Surreal_numbers_derivations_and_transseries","abstract":"Several authors have conjectured that Conway's field of surreal numbers,\nequipped with the exponential function of Kruskal and Gonshor, can be described\nas a field of transseries and admits a compatible differential structure of\nHardy-type. In this paper we give a complete positive solution to both\nproblems. We also show that with this new differential structure, the surreal\nnumbers are Liouville closed, namely the derivation is surjective.","authors":["Alessandro Berarducci","Vincenzo Mantova"],"meta":["March 2015Journal of the European Mathematical Society 20(2)","DOI:10.4171/JEMS/769","SourcearXiv"],"references":["243117968_Fields_of_surreal_numbers_and_exponentiation","230883487_On_generalized_series_fields_and_exponential-logarithmic_series_fieldswith_derivations","222095248_A_Note_on_Schanuel's_Conjectures_for_Exponential_Logarithmic_Power_Series_Fields","51967127_Toward_a_Model_Theory_for_Transseries","47338014_Hardy_type_derivations_on_fields_of_exponential_logarithmic_series","266267733_Foundations_of_analysis_over_surreal_number_fields","265549166_An_introduction_to_the_theory_of_surreal_numbers","246523838_Introduction_aux_fonctions_analysables_et_preuve_constructive_de_la_conjecture_de_Dulac","246485046_Integer_parts_of_real_closed_exponential_luelds","239595675_The_Elementary_Theory_of_Restricted_Analytic_Fields_with_Exponentiation","239578388_The_Rank_of_a_Hardy_Field","225129529_H-fields_and_their_Liouville_extensions","220316300_Every_Real_Closed_Field_Has_an_Integer_Part","44498189_Fonctions_d'une_variable_reelle_Theorie_elementaire","39278663_Levelled_O-minimal_structures","2831348_Maps_on_Ultrametric_Spaces_Hensel's_Lemma_and_Differential_Equations_Over_Valued_Fields","2213195_Exponential_algebraicity_in_exponential_fields"]}